</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uznailvh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Znail vh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 321<br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/16/02 2:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter balancing - drop rate of Dementing Visions</span><hr size=1> Three things. First is about the castersrealm boards. Those boards have a fairly bad reputation and I doubt verant follows them any more then I do.<br>
<br>
Secondly, enchanters arent the only ones with spells only a few may see. You should perhaps look up the rarity of GSS and EER.<br>
<br>
Thirdly, maybe you should try and lobby for spells over all to get less rare instead of only your class rare spell. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umeranaofvazaelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Merana of Vazaelle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/16/02 3:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter balancing - drop rate of Dementing Visions</span><hr size=1> Three replies:<br>
First - the enchanter board on casters realm is THE enchanter board. Once upon a time casters realm was only an enchanter site. They expanded to have information and boards for everything. But if you are an enchanter, and you want to discuss things with the best enchanters on all the servers, you go there. All attempts to start new boards have had poor results. In Verant's links of class specific boards, they list that site -- but you are right, they don't ever visit it. When the new keys interface was first introduced and bugged, they went to every class board to post to make sure people didn't delete their keys, but not ours. We have never had a visit of any kind from them that we are aware of. Feedback gets no-where. So, I do hope you forgive our intrusion, and allow us the hope that Verant might actually see this here.<br>
<br>
Second: The most recent patch &quot;balanced&quot; enchanter nuking abilities by upping the damage on this spell (and the ancient spell, which I won't go into). How can anything that only includes an ultra rare spell that very few enchanters on any server have be considered balancing?  Its not an issue of rare spells. Nobody has ever described GSS and EER as class balancing. I have no problem with rare spells. I have a big problem with their only answer to balancing being to increase the damage on an ultra rare spell.<br>
<br>
Third: Well, third was answered in second actually.<br>
<br>
The general point is that anything that is considered class balancing needs to be able to be acquired with a reasonable amount of difficulty by the majority of that class. I'm not saying it has to be vendor bought. I don't mind a reasonable amount of effort involved.  But a spell that drops extremely rarely off a mob that spawns once a week, is highly contested and requires an uber-guild to kill cannot be part of class balancing. This is true for any class, including wizards. So from this perspective, it is applicable here.  <br>
<br>
This is not the enchanters' only balance issue, and it probably isn't even be the biggest one. But the enchanters are fairly sure that the dev team does not read their board and is not aware of their issues. So again, I hope you pardon the intrusion.<br>
<br>
Merana, level 60 enchanter<br>
Laurelyn, level 44 wizard <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ullorianlanys.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llorian Lanys</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/16/02 5:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter balancing - drop rate of Dementing Visions</span><hr size=1> Yeah sorry to invade your board... i do read here sometimes but only lurk here...<br>
<br>
Casters realm main boards are horrid i agree, however the enchanter board is our &quot; graffes &quot; so to speak.  It is the one place where all enchanters go to congregate on the web, and has been since i started playing the game almost 3 years ago.<br>
<br>
Since it started as an enchanter site, all the enchanters still go there, even though it has been expanded till it is just a regular EQ site.  I have looked at most of the other boards there on casters realm, and they are pretty bad, but our enchanter one is pretty darn good.<br>
<br>
Verant knows about the board we are pretty sure, since they have it listed under class boards... but they never stop by and say anything in person like they do here.<br>
<br>
Sometimes we feel like lost stepchildren =P<br>
<br>
