     |  <a href="mailto:Cantatus@yahoo.com"><font color="#e09e6d">EMAIL</font></a></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=shakarr>Shakarr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/17/02 2:27 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter balancing - drop rate of Dementing Visions</span><hr size=1> I brought all my wife's enchanter spells (except KEI and Dementing Visions) for under 4k total in bazaar. One of my stun (stun???) costs more than that. Luck on your search for the spell, but I have little sympathy for you to be honest when our CRITICAL spells (nukes critical for chanters?) cost 25k+ and KEI is a meager 15k+ - god forbid if anyone ever sold EER or GSS what those would be worth.<br>
<br>
<br>
Shakarr Shockweaver <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ueqsharpy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>eqSharpy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/17/02 4:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter balancing - drop rate of Dementing Visions</span><hr size=1> Dang 15k for Kei? Nice! It is still 40-50k minimum on our server if you can find it at all.  Last time I saw it was in Bazaar for 85k a month ago, and it actually sold.  <br>
<br>
Class balance to give an enchanter a better nuke? Seems funny to me. If they wanted balance there would be no level caps on charm or mes (just immune) and all wiz spells would be unresistable (although partial damage like how melee damage works) Dire charm would be simply 15 level below you, and a level 51 spell. <br>
<br>
Not that Wiz spells are not rare and expensive.  The cost and rare nature of wiz spells is why team mana burn grows in popularity every day. They are not called team mana burn on my server, we have too many <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  One of my friends has 4 himself. But he has always been the power hungry roll to the newest power class type. So I don't consider him a Wizzard.<br>
<br>
Shaman spells were uber rare not very long ago, and when PoP comes out I am sure they will look at balancing a little more. Enchanters look like spell caps will give them the short end of the stick, and Wizzards really need to have thier Lure spells looked at now that the new resistance rates have changed. Mana cost halved maybe. <p><img src="http://softwareoutlet.com/images/dwarfrogue4.gif"><br></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=758.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=758.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=758.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=758.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=758.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=758.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"><